A four bedroom vacation rental situated in the breathtaking Alpine landscape of Vals, Switzerland. The house was designed by @bjarnemastenbroek of SeARCH & Christian Müller of CMA.

📷 @iwanbaan @plansmatter
📍Vals, Switzerland
